The limited edition Louis Moinet Memoris Superlight showcases a revolutionary approach to chronograph design. Its standout feature is the separation of the chronograph mechanism, consisting of 147 components, from the automatic movement, which contains 164 components. This innovative design places the chronograph at the top of the watch, with the automatic mechanism positioned beneath, enhancing functionality and visual appeal. This timepiece offers a mesmerising display of mechanical artistry.
